OL,3,CMan dies in collision on A-road after
OL,4,Ccar breaks down
OL,6,FA man has died following a collision
OL,7,Fon the A46 in Warwickshire after his
OL,8,Fcar broke down.
OL,10,FPolice were called to the southbound
OL,11,Fstretch of the road between Oversley
OL,12,FGreen and Salford Priors near Alcester
OL,13,Fshortly before 3.45am yesterday
OL,14,Fmorning, to reports a pedestrian had
OL,15,Fbeen hit by an HGV lorry.
OL,17,FOfficers say the man, who was in is
OL,18,F60s, is understood to have been
OL,19,Fwalking towards his car, which had
OL,20,Fbroken down, when the collision
OL,21,Fhappened.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
