OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1779714673
OL,3,CMan dies in collision on A-road after
OL,4,Ccar breaks down
OL,6,FHe died at the scene.
OL,8,FA 55-year-old man from Cornwall has
OL,9,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of causing
OL,10,Fdeath by dangerous driving. He remains
OL,11,Fin police custody.
OL,13,FA spokesperson from Warwickshire
OL,14,FPolice said: "Investigations are
OL,15,Funderway and we're asking anyone with
OL,16,Fdashcam footage of the collision, who
OL,17,Fwas driving along that stretch of road
OL,18,For who saw anything get in touch."
